high_descs: Walk forward and around the coffee table to the sofa
Pick up the left most pillow from the sofa
Turn left and walk forward to the right most arm chair
Put the pillow down on the arm chair
Turn right and walk back down to the right side of the sofa
Pick up the pillow from the sofa
Turn left and walk back over to the right most arm chair
Put the pillow on the chair to the right of the other pillow
anns.task_desc: Put the pillows on the arm chair

high_descs: Go around the black table to the sofa with white cushions.
Pick up the white cushion on the left.
Turn left and go to the arm chair on the right.
Place the cushion on the left side of the chair.
Turn around and go back to the sofa with a cushion on it.
Pick up the last white cushion on the sofa.
Go back to the arm chair with cushion on it.
Place the cushion on the right side of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Move the cushions on the sofa to the arm chair.

high_descs: Go past the coffee table across the room to the sofa.
Pick up the pillow on the middle of the sofa.
Turn left and go to the chair on the right.
Set the pillow on the left side of the chair.
Turn around and go back to the far side of the couch.
Pick up the pillow on the right side of the couch.
Turn around and go past the coffee table to the chair on the right.
Set the pillow down on the right side of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Set two pillows in the chair on the right.
